Hey guys,

For those who doesn't know: Smart DNS allows you to unblock websites, access streaming services such as Netflix, Hulu, Pandora, HBO and many others. One of the advantages over using a VPN that this won't slow your internet since it only proxy specific websites.

I initially built this for myself however it takes some resources so I thought I could have a few clients here using it. I can add sites on demand but the most important ones are already supported (as in the title).

I own a Roku device so that's supported for sure as well as computers. This can work with other devices too.

So anybody interested in just drop me a PM. As for the price I thought about something like 2.5USD monthly. (Negotiable)

